interactions.name: Download Seasonal Report

__ID_1__.name: Prepare report data
__ID_1__.description: Extract and format seasonal data for the report

__ID_2__.code:
const data = context.workflow['__ID_1__'].result; const content = `

${data.title}

Generated on: ${data.date}

Key Insights

  • Average Confidence Level: ${data.summary.averageConfidence}%
  • Highest Predicted Value: $${data.summary.highestPrediction}
  • Lowest Predicted Value: $${data.summary.lowestPrediction}
  • Overall Trend: ${data.summary.trend}

Monthly Breakdown

${data.data.labels.map((label, i) => ` `).join('')}
Month Actual Predicted Confidence
${label} $${data.data.actual[i].toLocaleString()} $${data.data.predicted[i].toLocaleString()} ${(data.data.confidence[i] * 100).toFixed(1)}%
`; return content;
